# Task

**Explore Pricing Plans After a Free Trial Offer**

As a potential customer,
I explore the pricing plans for Ahazou after considering a free trial,
so that I can decide which subscription option best fits my needs for social media content.

**Success definition:** Given I am on the Ahazou homepage and see the free trial offer
When I click on the 'concordo' button to accept cookies and then click on the 'planos e preços' link
Then I should be navigated to the pricing plans page for Ahazou where I can view various subscription options like Ahazou PRIME and Ahazou PRO, along with their features.

## Trajectory

**Step 1:**

**Url (before/after):** 

https://ahazou.com/

https://ahazou.com/
